  • How do I add Aerodrome Finance to MetaMask?

    MetaMask automatically displays popular tokens like Aerodrome Finance（AERO）within your wallet. If you are not seeing your AERO in MetaMask, you can manually add it using the "Add to MetaMask" button above, over the price chart. Please remember that you first need to install MetaMask extension if you are on a PC or Mac (desktop computer). If you are on mobile, please check out our MetaMask Support guide here for more info.

  • What is Aerodrome Finance's all-time low?

    The all-time low of Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is $0.00001861.

  • What is Aerodrome Finance's all-time high?

    The all-time high of Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is $2.32.

  • How do I buy Aerodrome Finance?

    Buying Aerodrome Finance (AERO) in MetaMask wallet is speedy, simple, and safe. You can buy Aerodrome Finance (AERO) tokens directly in MetaMask using payment methods like a credit card, debit card, bank account, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal. There’s no need for centralized exchanges. Select from thousands of your favorite tokens to buy on over 15 networks including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Linea, Base, and more.

  • How do I sell Aerodrome Finance?

    MetaMask makes it easy to sell your Aerodrome Finance (AERO) and convert your crypto to cash. You can exchange from MetaMask wallet directly to your debit card, credit card, PayPal, or bank account. By removing unnecessary steps and cutting excess fees, offramping your digital assets is fast and simple.

  • How do I swap Aerodrome Finance?

    Swapping AERO is simple and cost-effective with MetaMask. Choose from thousands of your favorite tokens across ten networks including Ethereum, Solana, Linea, Base, and Arbitrum. MetaMask Swaps also include gas fees right in your quotes, making swapping crypto as smooth as can be.

  • How do I bridge Aerodrome Finance?

    Bridging crypto across chains allows you to move tokens from one network to another. With MetaMask, bridging Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is easy, secure, and cost-effective. Our aggregator finds the most efficient routes to move your digital assets from one chain to another. And with cross-chain swapping, bridging and swapping can take place at the same time in a single transaction. Meaning: instead of bridging AERO from chain A and wrapping or unwrapping it on chain B, you can swap AERO from chain A to a second token on chain B, all in one move.

  • What can you do with Aerodrome Finance?

    With Aerodrome Finance, you can send and receive AERO, the network’s native token, and use it to pay transaction fees on certain networks. AERO is supported in decentralized apps for trading, staking, yield optimization, and payments. You can participate in DeFi protocols, bridge assets between networks, or use AERO in select web3 financial strategies, all with Ethereum-compatible speed and flexibility.

  • What is the price history of Aerodrome Finance?

    Today, September 8, 2025, the price of Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is $1.18. The all-time high of Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is $2.32. The all-time low of Aerodrome Finance (AERO) is $0.00001861. Aerodrome Finance (AERO)’s market capitalization is $1,059,168,579.00.

  • How do I trade Aerodrome Finance for other cryptocurrencies?

    Trading Aerodrome Finance (AERO) for ETH, WBTC, or SOL can be done directly in MetaMask. For more information on how to swap AERO, head to MetaMask Support.
